{
  "text": "I don't know if you can comment on the difficulty we will have in making the Law of One available to those who would require it or want it. It's not something that is easy to disseminate to those who want it at this time. I am sure there are many, especially the wanderers, who want this information. But we will have to do something else in order to get it into their hands in the way of added material, I'm afraid. Is it possible for you to comment on this? I am rock. It is possible.",
